            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            大盘分析（一）：从深成指看两市砸锅卖铁买股票的点位          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                      anmin0001                                  </span>                                                              <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                安民Anmin0001深度分析              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">安民Anmin0001深度分析</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">anmin0001gzh</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">活跃于网络20年，炒股30年。拿低定位守正，以高成长布局，且搏未来。</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       autoTypeSetting24psection            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden; user-select: none; -webkit-user-select: none;"><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">这篇文章的总体思路是，今年是筑大底之年，我们团队想从极具代表性的深成指走势图中，用技术分析的思路和方法，寻找到合理的左侧交易点位、右侧交易点位、加仓点等等。<br><br></span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 24px;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 宋体;">一、今年是筑大底之年</span></strong></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">先说说我们团队的观点：</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">1</span></strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">．今年两市是筑大底的大年</span></strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"></strong></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">也即今年沪深股指会找到一个大级别的低点。这个低点应该跟上证指数</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">1994</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">325</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">1996</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">512</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2005</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">998</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2008</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">1664</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2013</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">1849</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点一个级别，极有可能以后很多年都再难见到今年的大底。原因主要是三个：</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">）上证</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">50</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">、沪深</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">300</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">这两大指数连续三年收阴</span></span></strong><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">，这在历史上属于少见，仅此一次；不可能第四年收阴。</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">）两市主要指数季线指标都在低位。</span></span></strong><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">比如沪深</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">300</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">、上证</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">50</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">、深成指、深综指、中小</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">100</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">、创业板指、国证</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">A</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">指，特别是沪深</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">300</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">、上证</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">50</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">、深成指、中小</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">100</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">、创业板指，在我写这文章时，上证</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">50</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">季线慢速</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">KD</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">K</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">值为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">10.93</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">，为历史最低值。上证</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">50</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">历史上</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">,</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">季线</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">KD</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">K</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">值低于</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">20</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">的只有</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">4</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">次，分别是</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2005</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年第三季度</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">,</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">17.73;2012</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">9</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">,13.48;2014</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">6</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">,18.31;</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">再就是这次，现在是</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">10.93</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2024</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月底收盘<span style="color: black;">数据</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;color: black;">K</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;color: black;">值为</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">12.88</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">；它的最终值要等</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">3</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月底季线收盘才知道。沪深</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">300</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">历史上，只有</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">3</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">次，分别是</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2005</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">3</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">10.58</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">；</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2012</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">9</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">,16.33;</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">现在</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">,10.47</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">；为历史最低值。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2024</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月底<span style="color: black;">收盘时为</span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;color: black;">11.03</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;color: black;">；</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">它的最终值要等</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">3</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月底季线收盘才知道。大家可以看看历史上，这两个指数季线</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">K</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">值出现最低值以后的走势，都是一轮上涨。以前我一直在说，上证</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">50</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">是两市的重心，实际上沪深</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">300</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">也是，它们代表着两市的大盘股，在沪深市场具有很大的代表性。从这两大指数的历史表现来看，今年构筑大底是正常现象。</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">给两个图</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">:</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">上证</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">50</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">指数季</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">K</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">线图</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;"><br></span></span></section><section style="text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100002837" data-ratio="0.8385167464114832" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/dz1cb5niaGib6OZr53wZ2iaWicZGbZ4WRZwic2r28ibybjMRdN9Eur2SlvoHMHZXr3Uq4vdk0KeP2XmKqL2m5967KKicw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="836" style=""></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">沪深</span><span lang="EN-US" style='font-size: 14pt;font-family: "Calibri", sans-serif;'>300</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">季</span><span lang="EN-US" style='font-size: 14pt;font-family: "Calibri", sans-serif;'>K</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">线图<br></span></span></section><section style="text-align: center;line-height: 2em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img" data-galleryid="" data-imgfileid="100002838" data-ratio="0.9318181818181818" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/dz1cb5niaGib6OZr53wZ2iaWicZGbZ4WRZwicuuOibKMdic5AE5WrOUtRS4WgDVMrH5dSwLWUL8Bwrp4D9hn6QXGiaAXNQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="png" data-w="836" style=""></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">（</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">3</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">）基本面因素。</span></span></strong><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">我上个月的文章</span><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2NDk4MjQ1OQ==&amp;mid=2247486300&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=8dc0b654b85e217144f329258ec66b31&amp;chksm=ce604f88f917c69e29f6f92aeeeac6cc2ff6c846696e81c8c09772380f5575ae96d099e1139b&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="《对话安民Anmin0001(一):投资大时代，不要放过那种改变您一生命运的大机会》" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="2"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">《对话安民</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">Anmin0001(</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">一</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">):</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">投资大时代，不要放过那种改变您一生命运的大机会》</span></strong></a><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">中讲得非常清楚，导致后面</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">A</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">股牛市的原因和内在逻辑链条，宏观基本面和中微观基本面，还有估值因素，都有利于筑大底。包括近期的走势，高股息股指数</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">880845</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">为啥能创历史新高？对这个现象我们在文章中是讲了内在逻辑的，有清晰的论述的。</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2</span></strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">．不会同步见底</span></strong><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"></strong></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">不同板块见底时间不同。关于这点，可以参看我</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">1</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">15</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">日的文章，</span><a target="_blank" href="http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=Mzg2NDk4MjQ1OQ==&amp;mid=2247486382&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1e6a37d5a13f48435c123e994d2d7207&amp;chksm=ce604f7af917c66cfd9a6337d1c458ce4af4a44afbca3e971fb2f50b0e55e2a1119a92713413&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect" textvalue="《底部最重要的素质就是耐心，也需要技术》" linktype="text" imgurl="" imgdata="null" data-itemshowtype="0" tab="innerlink" data-linktype="2"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">《</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;color: black;background: white;">底部最重要的素质就是耐心，也需要技术</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">》</span></strong></a><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">。这次见底，可能会走类似</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2012</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年到</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2014</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年大底的那种走势，不同板块见底时间相差比较大。</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">但总体而言，今年的战略任务就是找底。我前期有言，对我们这个年龄阶段的人来说，未来的牛市极有可能是我们这一辈子最为重要的牛市，很有可能是最后一次大牛市。因此我一直在讲，今年找底，找得到也得找，找不到也得找。</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">但好在深成指历史走势提供了极好的参照。</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">另外解释一点，为什么大家都觉得我总在讲底但底部总没有来到。那是我们和大家的风格根本不同。很多散户做股票，是今天进明天出，用我的话说就是超短线，这个并不是我们的重点，我们的重点是找一个确定性的大底，做一轮<strong>中级行情</strong>。而且在我的语言体系中，所谓中级行情，像</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2005</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">998</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点到</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2007</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">6124</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点是中级行情，同样地，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2013</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">1849</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点到</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2015</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">5178</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点也是一轮中级行情。当然有些特别的板块和个股，我们也做更大级别的行情，那就是有行业上升大趋势的板块，操作周期会更长。深成指</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2021</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">18</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">日最高点</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">16293</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点，它这三年来的下跌，对我们来说，底部只有一个，就是今年出现的最低点，才是我们所要寻找的大底。当我写到这里时，深成指即时的点位是</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">8340</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点，最低</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;color: black;">8208</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;color: black;">点</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">，跌了</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">8085</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">点，跌幅</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">49.62%</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">，但这里有可能并不一定是大底。<br><br></span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2022</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">4</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">2022</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">11</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">月，我们都抄过底，但那里都不是大底，都是短中期的底部。我们只把它们当作短线来做，有盈利就走了。包括我们在博文中讲到过的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">600050</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">、</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">002624</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">、电影股等等，盈利了最后都走了。但今年要找到的底部，跟前期找到的底部，根本就不是一个级别，我们操盘的周期到时也会有极大的差别。</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">一轮中级大行情，底只有一个，顶也只有一个。上海和深圳股市的上涨，经常一涨两年到两年半，最长</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">41</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">个月；一跌长的</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 14pt;">4</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">年，短的也有两年左右。我们所谓的大底，就是针对这个周期的，这是我们所谓的中级行情。</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">我们有时也做超长线投资，那个是产业周期，时间更长。但那类投资不是特别多，这个要看特别情况，要看具体到哪个行业。</span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 1px;">比如地产行业，尽管我们团队写了很多文章谈房地产，但我有好多年都没有再碰过。<br></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 1px;"><br><mpchecktext><br></mpchecktext></span><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;"></span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 24px;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 24px;font-family: 宋体;">二、左侧交易，深成指什么点位可以砸<span style="letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 24px;color: black;">锅卖铁买股票</span></span></strong></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 1px;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">我们给几个图</span><span lang="EN-US" style='font-size: 14pt;font-family: "Calibri", sans-serif;'>,</span><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;">再给出各月、各周和每个交易日的<strong><span style="color: red;">点位数据</span></strong>。<br></span></span></section><section style="line-height: 2em;"><strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 1px;">（一）大三角形与季线技术指标</span></strong><span style="font-size: 14pt;font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 1px;"></span></section><p class="js_pay_preview_filter"><mp-pay-preview-filter data-offset="24"></mp-pay-preview-filter></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="685134783" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
